title: [Teorainn Dale, Birch Copse]
description: The chalky white bark of the birch trees contrasts pleasantly with the bright green of their leaves.  In places the papery bark has separated into curling strips, revealing an orangish inner bark.  Moonlight dapples the grassy path.
